{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0001","text":"喫我最不喜愛料理 喫到我歡喜","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["犧牲","遷就","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["料理","喜愛","歡喜"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,4,3,9,4,2,5,4,4,5,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hek3","ngo5","zeoi3","bat1","hei2","oi3","liu6","lei5","hek3","dou3","ngo5","fun1","hei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"喫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"最","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"喜愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"料理","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"喫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"歡喜","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以「喫」開頭，透過對比不喜愛的料理和喫到歡喜，表達為了迎合對方而改變自己，即使不喜歡也表現出喜歡。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0002","text":"有了你犧牲我習慣 免惹你生氣","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["犧牲","遷就","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["犧牲","習慣","生氣"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,5,3,3,5,2,4,5,5,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau5","liu5","nei5","hei1","saang1","ngo5","zaap6","gwaan3","min5","je5","nei5","sang1","hei3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"犧牲","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"習慣","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"免惹","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"生氣","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"使用「有了你」的句式，強調為了對方而犧牲自己的習慣，目的是避免引起對方不悅。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0003","text":"如果爭執只想討好你 不必講理","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["遷就","溝通","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["爭執","討好","講理"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,3,3,9,9,9,9,5,3,3,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","gwo2","zang1","zap1","zi2","soeng2","tou2","hou2","nei5","bat1","bit1","gong2","lei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如果","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"爭執","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"只想","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"討好","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"不必","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"講理","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"使用「如果」引導假設，表達在爭執時，寧願討好對方也不願講道理，顯示極度的遷就。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0004","text":"還期望穿衣穿到彷彿 很襯你","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["迎合","模仿","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["期望","穿衣","襯"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,3,3,3,4,9,3,9,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["waan4","kei4","mong6","cyun1","ji1","cyun1","dou3","fong2","fat1","han2","can3","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"還","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"期望","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"穿衣","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"穿","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"彷彿","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"很","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"襯","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「還期望」帶有諷刺意味，表達期望自己的穿著打扮都能迎合對方的喜好。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0005","text":"像你所講隨時要聽候","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["服從","等待","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["聽候","隨時"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,9,9,0,0,4,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoeng6","nei5","so2","gong2","ceoi4","si4","jiu3","ting1","hau6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"所","pos":"PART"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"隨時","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"聽候","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「像你所講」引述對方的話，表達隨時準備聽從對方吩咐的狀態。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0006","text":"你都講過愛是終身獻奉","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["承諾","奉獻","愛情觀"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["愛","終身","獻奉"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,9,4,4,2,3,3,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","dou1","gong2","gwo3","oi3","si6","zung1","san1","hin3","fung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"PART"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"終身","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"獻奉","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"引述對方對愛的定義，強調愛是終身的奉獻，為後文的對比鋪墊。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0007","text":"不計較亦無求 原來未足夠","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["付出","不被滿足","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["計較","無求","足夠"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,4,2,0,0,0,0,2,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","gai3","gaau3","jik6","mou4","kau4","jyun4","loi4","mei6","zuk1","gau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"計較","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"亦","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"無求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"原來","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"足夠","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「不計較亦無求」表達了無條件的付出，但「原來未足夠」揭示了這種付出並未得到對方的認可或滿足。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0008","text":"勉強遷就 只可加劇你渴求","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["遷就","加劇矛盾","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["遷就","加劇","渴求"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,0,3,2,9,9,3,2,5,4,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["min5","koeng4","cin1","zau6","zi2","ho2","gaa1","kek6","nei5","hot3","kau4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"勉強","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"遷就","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"加劇","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"渴求","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「勉強遷就」點明了遷就的無奈，而「只可加劇你渴求」則揭示了遷就反而讓對方索求更多，形成惡性循環。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0009","text":"依足你任何吩咐","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["服從","命令","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["吩咐","任何"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,5,2,0,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ji1","zuk1","nei5","jam6","ho4","fan1","fu6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"依足","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"任何","pos":"DET"},{"text":"吩咐","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「依足你任何吩咐」直接表達了完全服從對方的命令，沒有任何自主權。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0010","text":"更無權去攔住你拖手","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["失去自主權","無力感","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["無權","攔住","拖手"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,4,0,2,5,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mou4","kyun4","heoi3","laan4","zyu6","nei5","to1","sau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"更","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"無權","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"去","pos":"PART"},{"text":"攔住","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"拖手","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「更無權去攔住你拖手」進一步強調了失去自主權，甚至連阻止對方與他人親近的權利都沒有。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0011","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0011","text":"誰想到聽講聽教令我個性也生鏽","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["失去自我","個性磨損","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["聽講","聽教","個性","生鏽"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,4,3,9,3,4,2,5,4,4,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","soeng2","dou3","ting1","gong2","ting1","gaau3","ling6","ngo5","go3","sing3","jaa5","sang1","sau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"想到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"聽講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"聽","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"教令","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"個性","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"生鏽","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「誰想到」帶有驚訝和無奈，用「個性也生鏽」比喻長期的聽從導致自我僵化，失去活力。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0012","text":"誰想到只聽你話連自尊也再沒有","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["失去自尊","盲從","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["聽話","自尊","沒有"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,4,9,3,5,2,0,2,3,5,4,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","soeng2","dou3","zi2","ting1","nei5","waa6","lin4","zi6","zyun1","jaa5","zoi3","mut6","jau5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"想到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"聽","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"話","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"連","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"自尊","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「誰想到」再次表達驚訝和無奈，強調只聽對方話的結果是連自尊都喪失了。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0013","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0013","text":"馴服地吠不出口","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["壓抑","卑微","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["馴服","吠","出口"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,2,2,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seon4","fuk6","dei6","fai6","bat1","ceot1","hau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"馴服","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"地吠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"出口","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「馴服地吠不出口」用狗的行為比喻，表達被馴服到連不滿都無法表達出來的狀態。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0014","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0014","text":"令你我也看不起我遞上手","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["自卑","被看輕","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["看不起","遞上手"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,5,5,4,3,9,5,2,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ling6","nei5","ngo5","jaa5","hon3","bat1","hei2","ngo5","dai6","sau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"令","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"看不起","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我遞","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"上手","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「令你我也看不起我」表達了連自己都看不起自己，這種狀態甚至讓對方也看不起自己。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0015","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0015","text":"會拖多幾晝","structure":{"line_index":15,"char_count":5},"semantics":{"themes":["拖延","無奈","情感狀態"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["拖","幾晝"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["to1","do1","gei2","zau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"拖","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"多","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"幾晝","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「會拖多幾晝」表達了對這種無奈狀態的延續的預期，語氣中帶有疲憊。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0014","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0016","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0016","text":"像你所講難捱也接受","structure":{"line_index":16,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["忍耐","接受","愛情中的不對等"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["難捱","接受"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,9,9,0,0,5,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoeng6","nei5","so2","gong2","naan4","ngaai4","jaa5","zip3","sau6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"所","pos":"PART"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"難","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"捱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"接受","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「像你所講」再次引述對方的話，表達即使難以忍受，也只能接受。"},"source":{"title":"走狗","artists":["周柏豪"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2547","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0015","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_MjU0Nw_0017","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
